ks passed: `git diff --check -- crates/fwc/src/catalog.rs crates/fwc/src/readiness.rs` and `rustfmt --edition 2024 --check crates/fwc/src/catalog.rs crates/fwc/src/readiness.rs`. Remote verification is currently blocked by `rch exec` dependency preflight `RCH-E326`, which attempted to fail open to a local build; that fallback was explicitly terminated to honor the repo instruction to offload heavy Cargo work through `rch`. Workspace `cargo fmt --check` also reports unrelated pre-existing formatting drift in `connectors/jira/src/client.rs` and `crates/fwc/src/main.rs`.","created_at":"2026-03-26T21:20:04Z"}]}
